{"tid":2428341,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"［好痕好痕］有冇人有慢性風癩？","createTime":"2021-03-01T12:54:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T12:58:58.000Z","uid":90007,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ab3f82c2afd309e195e25b44b86238d38e52e32b","tid":2428341,"uid":90007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:54:39.000Z","msg":"一年前得左慢性風癩，中間無啦啦好返又復發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n晚晚到夜晚10點幾就黎料<br />\n依家靠啪抗敏藥先訓到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人好得返分享或者討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0014561f6536d5cb7a902daeba63267f545c126f","tid":2428341,"uid":194281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T14:03:26.000Z","msg":"你慢性風癩係點?<br />\n我皮膚敏感2日食一次抗敏藥<br />\n半年前就咁,食野敏感左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ebd523cbe9e01abfecd2189ecef8015299c1969","tid":2428341,"uid":90007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0014561f6536d5cb7a902daeba63267f545c126f","tid":2428341,"uid":194281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T14:03:26.000Z","msg":"你慢性風癩係點?<br />\n我皮膚敏感2日食一次抗敏藥<br />\n半年前就咁,食野敏感左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T14:15:47.000Z","msg":"巴打我都係每2日食一粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />2日後又會再起風癩<br />\n長期食會唔會死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31e05688e69d2896ee97682074fbd7fbcedebe38","tid":2428341,"uid":353508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T14:18:51